{"tid":2244940,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"比人帶去食黃店西餐 終於有間唔係比屎人食","createTime":"2020-10-16T00:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T21:27:17.000Z","uid":252492,"like":35,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb8489c13a30cb136b8225b17207ccd33080c4c","tid":2244940,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T00:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kxiD3gJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkxiD3gJ.jpg&h=a65d9872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前都有人帶我食過但果陣重係細鋪<br />\n今次轉左下午茶時間再去個鋪位大左3倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意粉同薄餅正常水準 薯條係一定要試<br />\n估唔到會咁既垃圾場既鋪食到咁高水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要唔似其他黃店比屎人食劏水魚<br />\n埋單好似先每人6x<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844da4b850d000e06cc3c2f6927d7e17332a49ea","tid":2244940,"uid":252492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbb8489c13a30cb136b8225b17207ccd33080c4c","tid":2244940,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T00:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kxiD3gJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkxiD3gJ.jpg&h=a65d9872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前都有人帶我食過但果陣重係細鋪<br />\n今次轉左下午茶時間再去個鋪位大左3倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意粉同薄餅正常水準 薯條係一定要試<br />\n估唔到會咁既垃圾場既鋪食到咁高水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要唔似其他黃店比屎人食劏水魚<br />\n埋單好似先每人6x<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T00:30:31.000Z","msg":"重有跟餐果3杯野飲同牛角包未影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aef4f07d68776a5117509c3b159a55340f136b","tid":2244940,"uid":372032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T00:31:05.000Z","msg":"Where"},{"pid":"1627b65efa7afa33194d26989eb58f1f